I will listen attentively to the customer's concerns, ask clarifying questions to understand their issue, and provide clear and concise information about our products or services. If necessary, I will take or enter orders, cancel accounts, or escalate the issue to a supervisor or specialized team to resolve the complaint. My goal is to provide a positive and helpful experience for the customer, resolving their issue efficiently and effectively.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
